videos.headline: Evans Kipruto throws down a powerful breakaway slam
videos.description: Calvin Wishart finds Evans Kipruto on the breakaway for a powerful two-handed slam for the Gauchos.

tracking.trackingName: **UNPUB 6/30** NCB_One-Play (Evans Kipruto throws down a powerful breakaway slam) 2023/3/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Caleb Lohner throws down the tomahawk dunk for Baylor
videos.description: Adam Flagler finds Caleb Lohner rolling to the basket and hits him in stride for a powerful one-handed slam.

tracking.trackingName: **UNPUB 6/30** NCB_One-Play (Caleb Lohner throws down the tomahawk dunk for Baylor) 2023/3/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Evans Kipruto throws down a powerful and-1 flush
videos.description: Ajay Mitchell dimes Evan Kipruto with a beautiful no-look bounce pass for a two-handed and-1 dunk vs. Baylor.

tracking.trackingName: **UNPUB 6/30** NCB_One-Play (Evans Kipruto throws down a powerful and-1 flush) 2023/3/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Baylor's Dale Bonner checks in with his jersey inside out
videos.description: Dale Bonner suffers a wardrobe malfunction as he tries to check in with his jersey inside out.

tracking.trackingName: **UNPUB 6/30** NCB_One-Play (Baylor's Dale Bonner checks in with his jersey inside out) 2023/3/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Caleb Lohner caps off a big Baylor run with a corner 3
videos.description: Dale Bonner finds Caleb Lohner in the corner for a wide-open corner three to add onto the Bears' lead.

tracking.trackingName: **UNPUB 6/30** NCB_One-Play (Caleb Lohner caps off a big Baylor run with a corner 3) 2023/3/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Miles Norris gets a friendly bounce on the tip in for UCSB
videos.description: Ajay Mitchell tries to get an entry pass into Miles Norris, who accidentally tips it in for a Gauchos bucket.

tracking.trackingName: **UNPUB 6/30** NCB_One-Play (Miles Norris gets a friendly bounce on the tip in for UCSB) 2023/3/17 ESHEET
